    <p><span>The Swordsmith Village Arc antagonists.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Aniplex [274 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sony-group-corporation/sony-music-entertainment-japan/aniplex">Aniplex</a> and developer <a title="Companies > CyberConnect2 [613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/cyberconnect2">CyberConnect2</a> have released two new characters trailers for <em><a title="Games > Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - The Hinokami Chronicles 2 [7 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/demon-slayer-kimetsu-no-yaiba-the-hinokami-chronicles-2">Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba – The Hinokami Chronicles 2</a></em>, introducing Gyokko and Hantengu. <span id="more-956236"></span></p><p><em>Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba – The Hinokami Chronicles 2</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,210 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,000 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [27,880 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [13,897 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [16,916 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [22,811 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2928600/Demon_Slayer_Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_The_Hinokami_Chronicles_2/" target="_blank">Steam</a> on August 1 in Japan and August 5 in the west.</p><p>Watch the trailer below. View a new set of screenshots <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/gallery/demon-slayer-kimetsu-no-yaiba-the-hinokami-chronicles-2/april-6-2025/">at the gallery</a>.</p><h2><span>Character Trailer #08: Gyokko</span></h2><p><iframe title="家庭用ゲーム「鬼滅の刃 ヒノカミ血風譚2」キャラクター紹介映像08・玉壺" width="500" heigh