            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gematsu.com/2025/04/marathon-gameplay-reveal-showcase-set-for-april-12<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p><a title="Companies > Bungie [224 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sony-group-corporation/sony-interactive-entertainment/bungie">Bungie</a> will host the Gameplay Reveal Showcase for science-fiction player-versus-player extraction <a title="Genres > Shooter [4,058 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/shooter">shooter</a> <em><a title="Games > Marathon [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/marathon">Marathon</a></em> on <a href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20250412T1700" target="_blank">April 12 at 10:00 a.m. PT / 1:00 p.m. ET</a>, the developer announced. You will be able to watch it on <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@MarathonTheGame" target="_blank">YouTube</a>, <a href="https://twitch.tv/marathonthegame" target="_blank">Twitch</a>, and <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@marathonthegame" target="_blank">TikTok</a>. <span id="more-956233"></span></p><p><em>Marathon</em> will be available for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,210 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,000 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [22,811 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3065800/Marathon/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Steam</a>. A release date has yet to be announced.</p><p>Watch a “save the date” trailer below.</p><h2><span>Save the Date Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="Marathon | Save the Date Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/PZUv1-qR1Aw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
